{"tid":1796523,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"政府譴責平安夜暴力及破壞行為","createTime":"2019-12-24T16:17:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T19:14:45.000Z","uid":216992,"like":32,"dislike":246,"uniUserReply":103,"replies":[{"pid":"6a4f5d9c58bdbce7f984df36deedb61ed5445a70","tid":1796523,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:17:05.000Z","msg":"政府譴責平安夜暴力及破壞行為<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n　　政府今日（十二月二十四日）嚴厲譴責蒙面暴徒於平安夜晚上在港九新界多區，包括尖沙咀、旺角、沙田和元朗等多個地點非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n　　政府發言人説，暴徒破壞交通燈、設傘陣、堵路、破壞商場店舖、縱火，甚至衝擊警務人員。這些行為嚴重擾亂社會秩序，影響市民歡度佳節，破壞節日氣氛，實在令人憤慨。<br />\n<br />\n　　在尖沙咀區，有人揮動港獨旗幟。發言人表示，提倡香港獨立不符合香港特別行政區在《基本法》下的憲制及法律地位、不符合香港社會的整體和長遠利益，亦與國家對香港既定的基本方針政策相抵觸。<br />\n<br />\n　　發言人續說，面對暴徒行為，警方為保護市民安全，必須嚴正果斷執法，拘捕違法人士。<br />\n  <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年12月24日（星期二）<br />\n香港時間23時57分"},{"pid":"08a78405bc09581141e2acd7bb45a3a82d1adee4","tid":1796523,"uid":211935,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:19:14.000Z","msg":"noted"},{"pid":"cb89718e95d97fb91237293b81bce6ed049745bb","tid":1796523,"uid":30506,"like":89,"dislike":0,"score":89,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:19:40.000Z","msg":"已經分唔到係真定作<br />\n真係係人都寫到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55b81692e6832e2ee592d41e218dbd42d851375","tid":1796523,"uid":11001,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:19:55.000Z","msg":"講緊班武裝份子？"},{"pid":"504b29ed1cfba691b1e645f5cea980aa6309e063","tid":1796523,"uid":178108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:19:58.000Z","msg":"閲"},{"pid":"f8aaab7ecf2d7a0ceebe37509b2f8a14a10c05ef","tid":1796523,"uid":184261,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:20:06.000Z","msg":"套落黑警到都幾match"},{"pid":"7bac69a52e0686143293dd871b0d6d6217b7ecfb","tid":1796523,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:20:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警暴不止，反抗不息</span></strong></span><br />\n<blockquote>面具1個10hkd，<br />\n假設黃店全部以10hkd購入，<br />\n然後全部以10HKD 賣出，<br />\n同時提供黃店（所有食肆／商舖）優惠話，<br />\n食肆：付費時出示面具可以每人頭面具數，每人減5HKD<br />\n商舖：付費滿50HKD出示面具可全單減5HKD，<br />\n你話有冇得諗？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q973eDC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq973eDC.png&h=1d34a395&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n[商業奇才]惠顧滿50HKD出示V煞面具全單減5HKD, 有無得諗？<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1796489/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1796489/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"9915aab95ee07f434d76d3d79c5d8a714a3f58df","tid":1796523,"uid":338743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:20:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd90da33bf1f1ed2b279f363b3ba3f2ec6a86775","tid":1796523,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:20:25.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"458aeff99652ddb6b4dc5471df5c0a778f51583d","tid":1796523,"uid":116054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:20:33.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"652577f84ca0ead160c16fce1855edab01c591b1","tid":1796523,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:20:36.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"a758310345031714e508f202321c39ed7183494f","tid":1796523,"uid":34777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9915aab95ee07f434d76d3d79c5d8a714a3f58df","tid":1796523,"uid":338743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:20:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:20:46.000Z","msg":"比藍絲打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1dff0d8df91f553227a360c306387cef9bacf2","tid":1796523,"uid":10509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:21:00.000Z","msg":"重點係港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b80b736fd14d042804c672ea86af538fdade92a","tid":1796523,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"scor